    <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
      <p>Samuel Solomon was a professor of political science at the Eastern Michigan University.</p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
      <p>As a teacher of government at Eastern Michigan University, Samuel Solomon clipped articles from Michigan newspapers about Michigan governors and state government. The clippings have been arranged chronologically and provide a valuable resource on state government issues and party politics in the period of 1948 to 1984.</p>
    </scopecontent>
